@@TJvRunOnStartup
Description:
This component allow you to make your Application start with windows once, always,...

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvRunOnStartup.GetRun@string
Description:
This function will return true if the title you give is associated with an Application who'll run with windows

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvRunOnStartup.GetRunOnce@string
Description:
This function will return true if the title you give is associated with an Application who'll run once

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvRunOnStartup.SetRunOnStartup@string@string@Boolean@Boolean
Description:
This procedure will make your program start with windows

Parameters:
Title: 
is the title of your Application
CommandLine: 
is the path of your Application (ex: d:coucou.exe)
RunOnce: 
Put this variable to true if you want to run once your Application on startup
Run: 
put this variable to true if you want to start your Application with windows

